@HillaryClinton We know Hillary, you think if Biden was President we'd have zero cases of COVID-19 & everything would've worked like clockwork. 

In reality we would have thousands dead, been shut down for months, gone trillions more in debt & be heading into the next Great Depression. #NoJoe https://t.co/nSa4e3guNs
